parameters:
\SE[24]I don't particularly like the scenery from here...
\SE[38]The snow swallows both purity and impurity, covering
everything. It has quite an elegant atmosphere, don't you think?

\SE[74]... I see. But I didn't come here for sightseeing. \SE[3]
So, what are the conditions you're talking about?

\SE[38]It's a simple condition. \SE[37]Just fight me and take it
by force. However, Laura... \SE[38]It must be done with your own
power.

\SE[5]Yeah, it's fine. I'm prepared for that level of resolve.
\SE[0]...Vita, Vega. Step back.

\SE[39]You're quite quick to understand... \SE[2]Then, let me
invite you to my world...

\SE[90]I have no choice but to leave it to you... \SE[91]Do it
properly... Laura...
